    "data": [
        {
            "title": "銷毀118萬劑過期復必泰二價疫苗 佔採購量逾6成 議員質疑浪費公帑",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"銷毀118萬劑過期復必泰二價疫苗 佔採購量逾6成 議員質疑浪費公帑\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/ce8f259178ac012b3021ca8593e45583/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250411/_2025041118544469841.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">銷毀118萬劑過期復必泰二價疫苗 佔採購量逾6成 議員質疑浪費公帑</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>政府早前回應立法會提問時指，截至2月底約118萬劑復必泰二價疫苗，因於倉庫到期需作銷毀，佔該疫苗採購量約62.1%。立法會今日（11日）舉行財務委員會特別會議時，選委界議員陳凱欣質疑銷毀疫苗是浪費公帑。醫衞局解釋比例高因基數小。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4190353/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"選委界議員陳凱欣質疑銷毀疫苗是浪費公帑。資料圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b1cc212226c8325471aea59a91874b39/2025-04/NW241016HON002.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        選委界議員陳凱欣質疑銷毀疫苗是浪費公帑。資料圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4190350/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"政府指，截至2月底約118萬劑復必泰二價疫苗因於倉庫到期需作銷毀。資料圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/16c295445df43dc34c4f06479f5359fa/2025-04/89607968746804.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        政府指，截至2月底約118萬劑復必泰二價疫苗因於倉庫到期需作銷毀。資料圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4190351/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"立法會今日（11日）舉行財務委員會特別會議時，陳凱欣質疑銷毀疫苗是浪費公帑。資料圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/5adb082740e522ead983899d2df49d95/2025-04/DNSJ1105THKMA020.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        立法會今日（11日）舉行財務委員會特別會議時，陳凱欣質疑銷毀疫苗是浪費公帑。資料圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4190356/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"醫衞局長盧寵茂。資料圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/2c2d3740a8decaf7d3dd8575e88e0bd2/2025-04/NJ240124LEGCO76.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        醫衞局長盧寵茂。資料圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4190375/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"盧寵茂稱，不要忘記「疫苗曾經一段時間真係周圍去搶。資料圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/07e60c0965b5e67993c04e5644685a5e/2025-04/0897468405_0.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        盧寵茂稱，不要忘記「疫苗曾經一段時間真係周圍去搶。資料圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>陳凱欣指，當局經常叫病人不要浪費、不要濫用，稱見到看到當局文件的答覆時「好心痛」，因當局答覆指118萬劑復必泰二價疫苗需要棄置。醫衞局長盧寵茂稱，不要忘記「疫苗曾經一段時間真係周圍去搶」，並強諮相關疫苗已經過期。\n\n</p>\n<p>陳凱欣反駁稱「過期前你都可捐出、接種的」，強調使用公帑購買疫苗，更引用盧曾說的詬反駁他，「用你的一句，不要浪費。」\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2063444/即時-港聞-銷毀118萬劑過期復必泰二價疫苗-佔採購量逾6成-議員質疑浪費公帑",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-11 18:56:28",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
