        {
            "title": "關稅戰︱特朗普遭惡搞變周星馳「唐伯虎」  吟詩「我笑他人看不川」︱多圖",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"內地網友惡搞特朗普。小紅書@小紅書651B4F57 / 言之宇宙\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/a55b92bb745ebc9ffaeccebcf7e7f4dd/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250411/_2025041118340793476.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">內地網友惡搞特朗普。小紅書@小紅書651B4F57 / 言之宇宙</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>美國總統特朗普（Donald Trump）4月9日宣布對不採取報復性行動的國家實施90天的關稅暫停，但日前上調對華關稅至125%，加上以打擊芬太尼為由加徵的20%，目前中國製造貨品關稅達145%。此舉惹怒中國官方，亦引發民間輿論。在內地社交平台，有多名網友惡搞特朗普，稱其為「關稅帝君」「萬稅（歲）爺」，指其「特離普（譜）」。\n\n</p>\n<p>在小紅書，有人製作了特朗普身著龍袍、手持關稅牌端坐的惡搞圖，被評論區網友奉為「千古名作」。圖中的「特朗普」左右側分別寫有「川心似海」「普天同稅」，其座下文字「普嚨宮」乍看令人一頭霧水，實則可謂「點睛之筆」。據悉，「普嚨宮」諧音類似台語的「噗嚨共」，意指某人做事粗心大意，沒頭沒腦，不按常理出牌。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"內地網友惡搞特朗普。小紅書@小紅書651B4F57\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/acb168c1582ec65924d098348767440c/2025-04/1b96eb2837b426d9250daca217e6e2f.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        內地網友惡搞特朗普。小紅書@小紅書651B4F57\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p> 另有網友製作了特朗普人物模型圖，圖中「特朗普」身著古裝，頭戴「川」字帽，手持「他人笑我（太瘋癲）」折扇，腳底則寫有「我笑他人看不川（穿）」，造型酷似周星馳經典作品《唐伯虎點秋香》其中一幕呤詩的場景。圖片下方評論紛紛讚歎製圖者巧思，直呼「壓力給到義烏」。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"內地網友惡搞特朗普。小紅書@言之宇宙\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b6f778cf9fa3548259adeec0c4942d03/2025-04/WhatsApp_2025-04-1112_20_38_d9a105e1.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        內地網友惡搞特朗普。小紅書@言之宇宙\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>此外，還有網友貼出意趣盎然的特朗普「撞臉」圖，有「特朗普」雞、「特朗普」狗、甚至「特朗普」毛刷......\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"北京動物園撞臉特朗普的紅腹錦雞。小紅書@多喜\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8c5dfe3a607bb86a1ed6c4431898a66f/2025-04/1eeec9efd57c5c393ad5d44b9c7e460.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        北京動物園撞臉特朗普的紅腹錦雞。小紅書@多喜\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"北京動物園撞臉特朗普的紅腹錦雞。小紅書@多喜\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/baed783b546f814c9de50927c3244cde/2025-04/8da9d87c77e06283eec2539852cd3d9.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        北京動物園撞臉特朗普的紅腹錦雞。小紅書@多喜\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"「特朗普」毛刷。小紅書@風清揚\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/9ad1974089cb6658692043d0a2328fca/2025-04/453ec95f091c474e0d3c55bc05a7f6d.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        「特朗普」毛刷。小紅書@風清揚\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"「特朗普」狗。小紅書@悟空\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3fb60d1660b648d9e98c6c8490e87f83/2025-04/13b5e861e126859cd35c3cbc9f8dcb7.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        「特朗普」狗。小紅書@悟空\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
